items.title: Awesome Selenium
items.content_text:
### Device Farms / Desktop GUI Automation (non-browser-centric)

*   [OpenSTF (⭐3.9k)](https://github.com/DeviceFarmer/stf) - A framework for running your own device farm, geared toward Android, but also iOS.

### Specifications / Desktop GUI Automation (non-browser-centric)

*   [The WebDriver Wire Protocol](https://www.selenium.dev/documentation/legacy/json_wire_protocol/) - All implementations of WebDriver that communicate with the browser, or a RemoteWebDriver server shall use a common wire protocol.

### Blogs / Desktop GUI Automation (non-browser-centric)

*   [Official Selenium Blog](https://www.selenium.dev/blog/) - The official blog by SeleniumHQ.

items.title: Awesome Newsletters
items.content_text:
### General Section / Svelte

*   [Pointer](https://www.pointer.io/). A window into what current and future CTOs are reading and thinking about. Super high quality engineering-related content only.

### Miscellaneous / Svelte

*   [rendezvous with cassidoo](https://cassidoo.co/newsletter/). A free weekly tech newsletter with the latest web development articles, a practice technical interview question of the week, a joke, some non-technical content, and more, arriving every Sunday night/Monday morning depending on where you are in the world.

items.title: Awesome Machine Learning
items.content_text:
### Python / General-Purpose Machine Learning

*   [Upgini (⭐333)](https://github.com/upgini/upgini): Free automated data & feature enrichment library for machine learning - automatically searches through thousands of ready-to-use features from public and community shared data sources and enriches your training dataset with only the accuracy improving features.
items.content_html:
Python / General-Purpose Machine Learning

  • Upgini (⭐333): Free automated data & feature enrichment library for machine learning - automatically searches through thousands of ready-to-use features from public and community shared data sources and enriches your training dataset with only the accuracy improving features.

items.title: Awesome Zsh Plugins
items.content_text:
### Themes / [superconsole](https://github.com/alexchmykhalo/superconsole) - Windows-only

*   [github (⭐3)](https://github.com/Debdut/github.zsh-theme/) - A GitHub-inspired theme. Shows decorators for (truncated) current directory, hostname and `git` status. Includes both light and dark modes and detects system settings for that on macOS and Linux.
items.content_html:
Themes / superconsole - Windows-only

  • github (⭐3) - A GitHub-inspired theme. Shows decorators for (truncated) current directory, hostname and git status. Includes both light and dark modes and detects system settings for that on macOS and Linux.
